Cell.Text: Are you Krev the Skinner? I'm here because I want to join the Silver Hand.

Cell.Text: I want to fight against the influence of Daedra in Skyrim.
S|This is an honor cause that every sons and daughters of Skyrim who wish to go Sovngarde one day, must fight for. | But I have more things to say before you can join us.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M10GMK_Topic03: I want to fight against the influence of Daedra in Skyrim.

Cell.Text: What things?

We fight against these beasts to cleanse this foul daedric disease that has taken the sanity of many of our brothers and sisters here on Skyrim. | But worst than that, have corrupted the souls of many sons of Skyrim, and take them away from Sovngarde in exchange of an ephemeral power in life. | But, you must be aware. No only beggars and forgotten people have lycanthropy here on Skyrim. | Many influential and powerful people have this curse... or "gift" as many of them say. | If you become a Silver Hand, you will have to fight not only physically, but also politically and economically powerful people. | After all I said, do you still want to become a Silver Hand?

Cell.Text: Yes, I do!

[S] Now, you are officially a silver hand initiate. Take this armor and shield. | They are not expensive ones, but are especially good to protect against the cold weather of the ice fields. | Also, take this weapon, a Silver sword. This one will protect you against foul creatures we fight against.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M10GMK_Topic05: Yes, I do!
